.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LNURL-INFO" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-lnurl-info \- show node Lightning Address and LNURL info
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-lnurl-info
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the node's identity and a derived Lightning Address.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"node_id":..., "alias":..., "lightning_address":..., "addresses":[...]}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-info (1),
.BR lightning-node-address-list (1)
